  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseCalendarService
    BaseCalendarService is an base implementation of the CalendarService.
    BaseExternalCalendarSubscriptionService  
    DailyRecurrenceRule
    DailyRecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a daily recurrence.
    DbCalendarService
    DbCalendarService fills out the BaseCalendarService with a database implementation.
    ExclusionRecurrenceRule
    ExclusionRecurrenceRule is a rule which excludes specific time ranges from a list of instances.
    ExclusionSeqRecurrenceRule
    ExclusionSeqRecurrenceRule is a rule which excludes specific sequence numbers from a list of instances.
    GenericCalendarImporter
    This class provides common importing functionality after a lower-level reader has taken care of the peculiarities of a given import format.
    MonthlyRecurrenceRule
    MonthlyRecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a monthly recurrence.
    MWFRecurrenceRule
    MWFRecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a weekly recurrence.
    RecurrenceInstance
    RecurrenceInstance is one instance of a recurrence sequence, with the time range and sequence # of the instance.
    RecurrenceRuleBase
    This is a common base for the daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly recurrence rules.
    SAK11204Fix  
    TThRecurrenceRule
    TTh RecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a weekly recurrence. repeating Tuesdays and Thursdays The recurrences happen on the same day-of-week, at the same time as the prototype.
    WeeklyRecurrenceRule
    WeeklyRecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a weekly recurrence.
    YearlyRecurrenceRule
    YearlyRecurrenceRule is a time range generating rule that is based on a yearly recurrence.
